                                    <h2>About The Project</h2>
                                        <!-- About us page of company here -->
                                        <p><strong>Mission:</strong> Deliver a complete platform rebuild for the Arkansas House of Representatives, replacing the legacy website with a modern Laravel-based solution featuring a comprehensive <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Content_management_system" target="_blank">Content Management System</a>. The CMS enables legislative staff to perform full <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Create,_read,_update_and_delete" target="_blank">CRUD</a> operations on representatives, news posts, events, and staff directories—with all changes automatically reflected on the public-facing website.</p>
